                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper reprints the New York Tribune's criticism of Gen. Canby's desire
                    to compel every Virginia State Legislature to take the iron-clad oath. "We hope
                    nothing will be done to drive into the opposition those Virginians who have
                    loyally accepted the new situation of affairs, and who stand ready to ratify the
                    fifteenth amendment."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
