                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>The paper reports that Henry Kenney, a local African American, was arrested
                    for drunken and disorderly conduct and fined $10. He was bound over to keep the
                    peace for a sum of $500.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
