                </names>
                <summary>Reuben Green who was arrested for killing Joseph Green at Pond Gap was
                    found guilty and sentenced to the State Penitentiary for 31 months.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>01</column>
